reviewText: Item arrived quickly and as described. Thanks!

Awsome , awesome docu film by Spurlock ..aka SUPER SIZE ME ...remember ? This was a fun little doc about how the comi con is a gate way to be found in that universe and how to make money and a living doing what they love from childhood .This is a fun and sometimes serious doc as u follow these certain types of people doing Sandiego comi con . I recommend this if u have ever been to a con or just have an interest what a con's like . enjoy
